item.title: Are Dogs Living a Secret Life in Their Sleep?
item.dc:creator: Soham Mahajan
item.description: Have you ever watched your dog twitch, bark, or move in their sleep and wondered what’s happening? Are they dreaming of chasing squirrels or reliving the day’s adventures?
